# Pole Position — local config (copy to .env; never committed).
#
# WRITING runs on your CLAUDE SUBSCRIPTION via the Agent SDK — do NOT add an Anthropic API key.
# Setting ANTHROPIC_API_KEY would override the subscription and bill you per token; the server
# deliberately ignores/drops it so writing always bills against your Claude plan.
#
# Optional — choose the writing model (default = your plan's default). e.g. top-tier prose:
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
#
# fal.ai IMAGE generation (Phase 3) DOES need its own key — fal isn't part of your Claude plan:
FAL_API_KEY=
